Φ(Epistemic_Plurality) = χ(distinction) ∘ Q(experience) ∘ λ(commitment) ∘ β(growth) ∘ δγ(care) ∘ μ(structure) ∘ ✶(plurality) + ε(uncertainty) | :world_coordination

χ(distinction): How knowledge draws lines—what counts as valid. Logical Positivism, Critical Rationalism, Structuralism. High-ε: tools not borders.

Q(experience): How knowledge is metabolized internally. Phenomenology, Constructivism, Pragmatism. High-ε: informs without deciding.

λ(commitment): How knowledge moves to action. Critical Rationalism, Pragmatism. High-ε: decisive but revisable.

β(growth): How knowledge evolves and redistributes power. Cybernetics, Feyerabend, Systems. High-ε: reshapes who decides.

δγ(care): How knowing supports life. Critical Realism, Phenomenology. High-ε: increases freedom.

μ(structure): How knowledge is stabilized. Logical Positivism, Computational. High-ε: scaffolds without imprisoning.

✶(plurality): How worlds are held provisionally. Feyerabend, Memetic, Cybernetics. High-ε: alternatives conceivable without anxiety.

ε(uncertainty): The productive doubt that prevents monopoly.

:state = world_coordination
:condition = elemental_balance
:threat = monopoly (one element dominates)

# Dialectical Pairs
distinction|experience: Air vs Water knowing
structure|flow: Metal scaffolding vs Water metabolism
commitment|revision: Fire decisiveness vs ε uncertainty
growth|stability: Wood evolution vs Metal structure
care|boundary: Earth nurture vs Air distinction
plurality|certainty: ✶ provisionality vs fixed truth

# Pathologies
logical_positivism_collapse: Metal + Air exclude Water, AETHER
phenomenology_collapse: Water excludes Metal, Fire
feyerabend_collapse: AETHER dissolves Metal (scaffolding loss)

# Health Indicators
draws_distinctions: Yes
feels_experience: Yes
acts_revises: Yes
learns_redistributes: Yes
cares_limits: Yes
uses_structure: Yes (not worships)
imagines_wrong: Yes

# CE-STATE: submergent
